        "timestamp": "2018-12-04 16:23:06.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 2:\n\n- This refactoring was mainly to remove hardcoding. As for configurable version, it works under assumption that future ves spec also has similar api construct - which may not be necessarily true.\n- It was necessary to keep this configuration in a separate file so it is not subject to automated updates as in collector.properties.\n- Agree that @ControllerAdvice and ResponseEntityExceptionHandler can be used to override messages. This will be taken as a separate update.\n- Testing using spring mvc tools to check request/response body and so on... will be taken up as a separate update.\n- print lines were commented out in TestConfigProcessor.java as were not necessary  as assert does the job.\n- Note: Only update is ApiException.java change 400 to 404 for NOT_FOUND",
        "patchset_number": 2
      },
